AmneziaWG is a VPN plugin for OPNsense that provides secure tunneling with
AmneziaWG 2.0 obfuscation (Jc, Jmin, Jmax, S1–S4, H1–H4, optional I1/CPS).
Multiple instances are supported, similar to the WireGuard plugin architecture.

Features:
- Multi-instance support for multiple AmneziaWG 2.0 connections
- Web-based configuration interface
- Built-in key pair generation
- Real-time status monitoring
- Configuration import from .conf (including bivlked/amneziawg-installer client exports)
- Automatic service management
- Status monitoring and statistics

Requires amnezia-tools and amnezia-kmod built for AmneziaWG 2.0.

WWW: https://github.com/amnezia/amneziawg 